OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779390672
OL,3,CNHS trust fires staff for
OL,4,Cinappropriate access to Nottingham
OL,5,Cattack records
OL,7,FNottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,8,FTrust (NUH) has dismissed 11 members
OL,9,Fof staff for accessing the medical
OL,10,Frecords of Ian Coates, Grace O'Malley-
OL,11,FKumar and Barnaby Webber.
OL,13,FStudents Webber and O'Malley-Kumar,
OL,14,Fand grandfather Coates, were stabbed
OL,15,Fto death by Valdo Calocane in
OL,16,FNottingham in 2023.
OL,18,FThe trust confirmed that "a further 14
OL,19,F(staff members) have had actions taken
OL,20,Fagainst them".
OL,26,@|D@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779390672
OL,3,CNHS trust fires staff for
OL,4,Cinappropriate access to Nottingham
OL,5,Cattack records
OL,7,FStaff included in these investigations
OL,8,Finclude doctors, nurses, registered
OL,9,Fmedical professionals and admin and
OL,10,Fclerical colleagues.
OL,12,F"I am truly sorry"
OL,14,FMedical Director at NUH Dr Manjeet
OL,15,FShehmar said:
OL,17,F"The families of Ian, Grace and
OL,18,FBarnaby have had to endure much pain
OL,19,Fand heartache, and I am truly sorry
OL,20,Fthat the actions of some of our staff
OL,21,Fhave added to that.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779390672
OL,3,CNHS trust fires staff for
OL,4,Cinappropriate access to Nottingham
OL,5,Cattack records
OL,7,F"To access the medical records of our
OL,8,Fpatients without a legitimate reason
OL,9,Fis totally unacceptable and we are
OL,10,Fdoing all we can to identify where and
OL,11,Fhow that has happened.
OL,13,F"I hope that the families, staff and
OL,14,Four communities feel reassured by the
OL,15,Foutcomes so far, that we are taking
OL,16,Fthis seriously and will continue to do
OL,17,Fso.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779390672
OL,3,CNHS trust fires staff for
OL,4,Cinappropriate access to Nottingham
OL,5,Cattack records
OL,7,F"We know that the vast majority of our
OL,8,Fstaff understand that appropriate
OL,9,Faccess is a fundamental principle of
OL,10,Four duty of care and know that it is
OL,11,Fessential that access to patient
OL,12,Frecords is lawful, justified, and
OL,13,Fdirectly related to their role.
OL,15,F"By accessing records inappropriately,
OL,16,Fstaff are damaging the valuable
OL,17,Fcontributions made by those colleagues
OL,18,Fproviding care for those patients.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779390672
OL,3,CNHS trust fires staff for
OL,4,Cinappropriate access to Nottingham
OL,5,Cattack records
OL,7,F"In those cases where it does happen,
OL,8,FI hope that this is a very clear
OL,9,Freminder that we will take appropriate
OL,10,Faction."
OL,12,FThe Trust said follow-up activity will
OL,13,Fnow take place with relevant
OL,14,Findependent regulators, such as the
OL,15,FNursing and Midwifery Council and
OL,16,FGeneral Medical Council.
OL,26,@rD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779390672
OL,3,CNHS trust fires staff for
OL,4,Cinappropriate access to Nottingham
OL,5,Cattack records
OL,7,FFurther investigations are ongoing
OL,8,Finto inappropriate access, including
OL,9,Finto the files of surviving victims,
OL,10,Fincluding Wayne Birkett, Sharon Miller
OL,11,Fand Marcin Gawronski.
OL,13,F"It's heartbreaking"
OL,15,FThe mother of Barnaby Webber, Emma
OL,16,FWebber, has said: "To learn that 11
OL,17,Fstaff have been dismissed and 14 faced
OL,18,Fdisciplinary actions is shocking.
OL,26,@xD@SOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779390672
OL,3,CNHS trust fires staff for
OL,4,Cinappropriate access to Nottingham
OL,5,Cattack records
OL,7,F"What is more shocking is the scale of
OL,8,Fmisconduct ` 150 members of staff
OL,9,Faccessed the records.
OL,11,F"The process is not yet complete so we
OL,12,Fanticipate these numbers to escalate
OL,13,Fconsiderably.
OL,15,F"The trust is also aware that we do
OL,16,Fnot accept their findings that 48
OL,17,Fmembers of staff had legitimate
OL,18,Faccess. The number is far too high.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779390672
OL,3,CNHS trust fires staff for
OL,4,Cinappropriate access to Nottingham
OL,5,Cattack records
OL,7,F"The rationale given for legitimacy
OL,8,Fdoes not stack up and we are formally
OL,9,Fchallenging this in order to
OL,10,Fscrutinise properly.
OL,12,F"It's heartbreaking that on top of our
OL,13,Ftragic loss, we've also had to face
OL,14,Fsuch appalling additional failures by
OL,15,Fmembers of staff who should know
OL,16,Fbetter. I'd ask them all to consider
OL,17,Fhow they would feel if it was their
OL,18,Fchild or father."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@QO]
